@{r}.asm inline assembler
@{c}@{h1}Contents

@{b}.asm@{ub} is an assembler which can assemble code embedded in a NextBASIC program, or
from a source text file.

@{" Running .asm " LINK RUNNING}

@{" Program format " LINK FORMAT}
